
required npm packages:
    1. express (A nodejs backend framework) - npm install express
    2. ejs (A web engine) - npm install ejs
    3. nedb (A lightweight database) - npm install nedb
    4. axios (A networking package for node) - npm install axios
    5. bcrypt (A password hashing package) -npm install bcrypt
    6. cookie-parser (A cookie manager for node js) - npm install cookie-parser

